banyan aerial roots hanging like natural curtains, realistic rough bark texture,

[Rendering Style] Unreal Engine 5 Lumen lighting, V-Ray architectural
visualization quality, PBR high-precision materials,
cinematic shallow depth of field (DOF), 35mm wide-angle lens, f/8 aperture,
rule-of-thirds composition, architecture occupies 60% centered upper frame,
warm gold dominant tone with lotus pink and water-blue accent colors,
4K ultra HD,
