Water/parasols: light water-blue (#5B8C7A range)
Accent: lotus pink (#E8A0B4) ONLY for node name text labels
Background houses: light gray (#D6E5E3) thin wash

[Legend Elements] Legend box (bottom right): 4 paving types (permeable brick/
gravel-grass/oyster terrazzo/bark mulch) + 5 furniture symbols (chess table/
curved bench/foldable stall/parasol/wood post fence),
no compass or scale bar (from SUAPP lineart),
30px margin on all sides, Logo bottom right (oyster shell outline + seal "五"),

Rendering style: architecture school watercolor wash, soft muted colors,
not over-saturated, paper texture + watercolor bleeding edges, 4K resolution,
```

### 10.5 立面图提示词（建筑立面生成）

> **出图工具**：Stable Diffusion + ControlNet Depth/Canny（输入CAD立面线稿）
> **建议尺寸**：1920×600（超宽横幅）

**正向提示词（中文）**：

```
景观建筑正立面图，人视角度从村路对面北向南看，长条形街景立面(约26m展开)，
珠海斗门五福村沿村路带状绿地，

【从左到右序列】
- 最左:青砖标识矮墙(H0.6m,旧木压顶)+3个抬升种植箱(紫苏/香茅茂盛轮廓)
- 树1:大榕树(H8-10m,半球形树冠,气根垂落),树旁为浅灰白透水砖铺装带
- 树2:榕树下见花岗岩棋盘桌(0.8m见方,H0.7m)+4个石凳(H0.45m)+对弈人形剪影
- 树3-4(中段核心):两棵榕树之间露出两把水蓝色渐变遮阳伞(伞径2.5m,H2.4m)+
  木质折叠推车吧台轮廓(H2.1m伞柱)+圆形蚝壳水磨石广场(地面浅色圆形区域)
- 树5:榕树下弧形木卡座靠背(H0.5m,150°弧线)+聊天人形剪影
- 树6(最右):大榕树+3根荔枝木立柱(H1.5m)+新植小莲雾树(H2.5-3m)+独坐长凳
- 地面层:三层渐变带清晰——透水砖(浅灰白)→碎石草缝(灰绿)→树皮(深褐)

【背景层】村路(宽4-5m,沥青路面)作为前景底边，
场地内各节点建筑/家具轮廓为中层，背景远处青砖民居屋顶轮廓线(约H5-7m)为上层，
房屋上方远山淡蓝轮廓+天空渐变(黄昏暖色),

【光影】柔和午后自然侧光(约下午3点,从左侧打入)，
建筑和家具投下短阴影在右侧地面，天空为暖白到浅蓝渐变(非黄昏，保留白昼清晰度)，

【人物剪影】所有人物为深灰剪影(成人H≈1.7m)，分布在:棋盘桌两侧×2，
茶寮推车旁×1，卡座上×2，木篱旁×1，用作比例参考,

【标注叠加(后期PS)】立面底部标注5个渐境节点名称和标高，
关键家具高度标注(棋盘桌H0.7m/遮阳伞H2.4m/木立柱H1.5m等)，
铺装渐变三层带用虚线分隔+文字Layer A/B/C,

【渲染】建筑学院派立面渲染，干净线条+柔色填充，非照片写实(偏向竞赛展板风格)，
横构图16:9→建议最终裁切为超宽幅，4K分辨率,
```

**正向提示词（English）**：

```
Landscape architecture front elevation, eye-level view from opposite side
of village road looking south, elongated streetscape elevation (approx 26m
unfolded), Zhuhai Doumen Wufu Village roadside linear greenspace,

[Left-to-Right Sequence]
- Far left: gray-brick marker wall (H0.6m, reclaimed wood cap) + 3 elevated
  planters (lush perilla/lemongrass silhouettes)
- Tree 1: large banyan (H8-10m, dome canopy, aerial roots hanging),
  beside: light gray-white permeable brick paving band
- Tree 2: under banyan, granite chess table (0.8m sq, H0.7m) + 4 stone stools
  (H0.45m) + seated human silhouettes playing chess
- Tree 3-4 (mid core): between two banyans, two water-blue gradient parasols
  (diam 2.5m, H2.4m) + wooden foldable drink stall cart outline (H2.1m pole) +
  circular oyster terrazzo plaza (light-colored circular ground area)
- Tree 5: under banyan, curved wooden bench backrest (H0.5m, 150° arc) +
  seated chatting human silhouettes
- Tree 6 (far right): large banyan + 3 lychee wood posts (H1.5m) + newly planted
  small lotus wax apple tree (H2.5-3m) + solitary bench
- Ground level: three gradient bands clearly visible—permeable brick (pale
  gray-white) → gravel-grass (gray-green) → bark mulch (dark brown)

[Background Layers] Village road (W4-5m, asphalt) as foreground bottom edge,
site furniture/architecture outlines as mid-layer, distant gray-brick house
rooflines (H5-7m) as upper layer, faint distant mountain silhouettes + sky
gradient (dusk warm tone) above houses,

[Lighting] Soft afternoon natural side light (~3PM, from left), buildings and
furniture casting short shadows to the right on ground, sky gradient from
warm white to light blue (daytime clarity, NOT full dusk),

[Human Silhouettes] All figures as dark gray silhouettes (adult H≈1.7m),
distributed at: chess table ×2 seated, tea stall ×1 standing, bench ×2 seated,
wood fence ×1 standing, serving as scale reference,

[Annotations (post-processing in PS)] Bottom: 5 gradient node names + elevation
marks, key furniture height labels (chess table H0.7m / parasol H2.4m /
wood posts H1.5m etc.), paving gradient three bands separated by dashed lines
+ Layer A/B/C text labels,

[Rendering] Architecture school elevation style, clean lines + soft color fill,
NOT photorealistic (competition board style), horizontal 16:9 composition—
recommend final crop to ultra-wide format, 4K resolution,
```

### 10.6 3D 模型提示词（腾讯混元 3D / Meshy.ai / TripoSR）

> **用途**：生成低面数3D模型用于 Remotion 动画和展板截图
> **输入**：配合场地线稿图/平面图+立面图作为 Image-to-3D 参考

**正向提示词（中文）**：

```
一个低面数(low-poly)游戏风格的珠海斗门五福村街角微景观完整场景，
长条形沿村路地块(长约26m,宽约7m)，

【树木】6棵榕树沿路边等距排列，半球形树冠(深绿色)，粗干(棕色)，气根悬挂，
树冠直径约5-6m，树干高约3-4m，树1-6自西向东均匀分布,

【建筑背景(新增)】场地北侧村路对面一排岭南青砖民居建筑群，
硬山坡顶+深灰瓦屋面+人字山墙轮廓，墙面为青灰色(#7B8B7A)，
檐下悬挂红色灯笼(小方块)，建筑高度约5-7m(低于榕树)，

【铺装渐变地面】从路边向内侧三层渐变:
- 最外层(沿路):浅灰白色透水砖纹理(#F2EFE9),
- 中间层:灰色碎石+绿色草缝混合纹理,
- 最内层:深褐色树皮/木屑覆盖(#8B6914),
- 路边无路牙，铺装边缘不规则锯齿过渡,

【各节点家具(自西向东)】
- 境一(树1旁):低矮青砖标识墙(H0.6m)+3个木质种植箱(深棕色方块,含绿色植物)
- 境二(树2下):方形花岗岩棋盘桌(0.8m见方,灰色)+4个方形石凳
- 境三(树3-4间):木质L形折叠推车吧台(棕色,H约2.1m伞柱)+
  两把圆形水蓝色遮阳伞(伞径2.5m)+圆形浅灰色水磨石广场(直径2.5m,贝壳纹理)
- 境四(树5周围):弧形木长凳(150°环抱,棕色)围绕树干
- 境五(树6旁):3根木立柱(H1.5m,深棕色)+一张长凳+一棵小型莲雾树(粉色花点)

【场景要求】适合导出为单个.glb文件，所有元素合并为一个mesh组，
无动画，低多边形风格(low-poly)，PBR材质，
缩放至真实尺寸比例(1 unit = 1 meter)，场景总包围盒约30m×15m×12m，
建议三角面数控制在50K-200K(适合Web/移动端展示),
树冠使用半透明面片+alpha贴图模拟榕树茂密质感,
```

**正向提示词（English）**：

```
A low-poly game-style Zhuhai Doumen Wufu Village street corner micro-landscape
complete scene, elongated linear plot along village road (approx L26m × D7m),

[Trees] 6 banyan trees evenly spaced along roadside, dome-shaped canopies
(dark green), thick trunks (brown), hanging aerial roots, canopy diameter
approx 5-6m, trunk height approx 3-4m, trees 1-6 distributed west to east,

[Architectural Background (NEW)] North side across village road: row of
Lingnan gray-brick residential buildings, pitched hard-mountain roofs with
dark gray tiles + wok-ear gable silhouettes, wall color gray-blue (#7B8B7A),
red lanterns (small blocks) hanging under eaves, building height approx 5-7m
(below banyan tree height),

[Paving Gradient Ground] Three bands gradient from roadside inward:
- Outer band (roadside): light gray-white permeable brick texture (#F2EFE9),
- Middle band: gray gravel + green grass joint mixed texture,
- Inner band: dark brown bark/wood chip cover (#8B6914),
- No curb at road edge, paving edges with irregular jagged transitions,

[Node Furniture (west to east)]
- Node 1 (beside Tree 1): low gray-brick marker wall (H0.6m) + 3 wooden planter
  boxes (dark brown blocks with green plant fills)
- Node 2 (under Tree 2): square granite chess table (0.8m sq, gray) + 4 square
  stone stools
- Node 3 (between Trees 3-4): wooden L-shaped foldable drink stall cart (brown,
  H~2.1m pole) + 2 circular water-blue parasols (diam 2.5m) + circular light
  gray terrazzo plaza (diam 2.5m, shell texture)
- Node 4 (around Tree 5): curved wooden bench (150° wrap, brown) around trunk
- Node 5 (beside Tree 6): 3 wooden posts (H1.5m, dark brown) + one bench +
  one small lotus wax apple tree (pink flower dots)

[Scene Requirements] Suitable for export as single .glb file, all elements
merged into one mesh group, no animation, low-poly style, PBR materials,
scaled to real-world dimensions (1 unit = 1 meter), total bounding box
approx 30m × 15m × 12m, recommended triangle count 50K-200K (suitable for
web/mobile display), banyan canopies using semi-transparent face cards +
alpha textures to simulate dense foliage quality,
```

