### 10.7 通用反向提示词 + 推荐参数配置

#### 反向提示词（Negative Prompt）— 适用于所有效果图

> **直接复制使用**。对于 SD/ComfyUI 可加上 `(worst quality, low quality:1.4)` 权重修饰。

```
(worst quality, low quality, blurry, distorted, deformed, disfigured:1.4),
extra limbs, bad anatomy, fused fingers, missing fingers, extra fingers,
mutation, mutilated, ugly, poorly drawn hands, poorly drawn face,
bad proportions, cloned face, watermark, signature, logo, text, date stamp,
username, artist name, frame, border, letterbox,

modern buildings, glass curtain wall, concrete, steel structure,
modern windows, modern doors, advertising billboards, neon signs,
street lamps (modern), cars, vehicles, asphalt road with markings,
traffic signs, parking meters, air conditioning units, satellite dishes,
Western architecture, European style, Gothic, Mediterranean style,

cartoon style, 2D flat, anime, illustration, sketch, wireframe,
line art, blueprint, untextured, white model, clay render,
grayscale, monochrome, black and white,

overexposed, underexposed, washed out, over-saturated colors,
harsh shadows, flat lighting, sterile lighting, fluorescent lighting,
repeating textures, visible seams, tiling artifacts,
symmetric (too perfect), structural asymmetry, proportion errors,
missing roof tiles, broken eaves, collapsed structures, ruins,

crowded scene (too many people), modern clothing (jeans, t-shirts, sneakers),
tourists with cameras, selfie sticks, smartphones,
plastic furniture, IKEA style, modern cafe furniture,
```

> **注意**：如场景需要特定人物（如 10.2 棋盘场景），需将上述反向提示词中的 `bad hands / extra limbs` 等人物相关项权重降低为 `:1.1` 或暂时移除。

#### 通用参数配置（适用于 ComfyUI / SD WebUI）

| 参数 | 推荐值 | 说明 |
|---|---|---|
| **采样器** | DPM++ 2M Karras / Euler a | 建筑写实效果好，细节丰富 |
| **采样步数** | 35-50 | 低于30细节不够，高于50收益递减 |
| **CFG Scale** | 7-9 | 7偏自然光感，9偏风格化 |
| **输出尺寸** | 1344×768(横) / 1024×1366(竖) / 1536×1024(方横) | 至少1024，底线768 |
| **高清修复** | 开启，放大2x，ESRGAN_4x | 去噪强度 0.35-0.45 |
| **Seed** | 随机出图4-8张 → 选择最佳构图 → 固定Seed微调 | — |
| **ControlNet** | Canny (0.75-0.85) + Depth (0.4-0.55) 双控 | 输入CAD线稿或手工草图 |

#### 不同场景的特别参数调整

| 场景 | CFG | 步数 | 特殊建议 |
|---|---|---|---|
| 10.1 茶寮主场景(日景) | 7.5 | 40 | 可加 `cinematic lighting` LoRA (权重0.3) |
| 10.1 夜景(可选) | 8 | 45 | 加 `blue hour` / `night` 标签，调低色温 |
| 10.2 棋盘场景(有人物) | 7 | 50 | 人物反向提示词降低，加 `candid moment` |
| 10.3 入口场景 | 7 | 35 | 干净画面，不加过重的风格化LoRA |
| 10.4 彩平图 | 5-6 | 25-30 | 低CFG保留软配色，加 `watercolor` LoRA |
| 10.5 立面图 | 7 | 30 | 配合CAD线稿ControlNet Lineart(0.9) |

#### 色彩一致性控制（关键！）

为保证所有效果图视觉统一：

```
所有正向提示词末尾统一追加色彩基调标签:
"...暖金色调为主(#D4A574受光/#2A1A0A阴影)，莲雾粉和水蓝色为点缀色，
蚝壳白基底(#F2EFE9)，青砖灰(#7B8B7A)建筑背景，莫兰迪柔色调，4K超高清"
```

> 若使用 **ComfyUI**，可开启 IP-Adapter 并以五福村参考效果图作为 style reference image（权重0.3-0.5），统一所有输出图的色调和氛围。

